<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Spaghetti Recipe</title>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- This is the main title of the recipe -->
    <h1>Simple Spaghetti Recipe</h1>

    <!-- This paragraph describes the recipe -->
    <p>
        This is my favorite spaghetti recipe because it is easy to cook and tastes really good.
        It is perfect for beginners and does not require too many ingredients.
    </p>

    <!-- This is the ingredients section -->
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>

    <!-- Unordered list for ingredients -->
    <ul>
        <li>200g spaghetti</li>
        <li>2 cups tomato sauce</li>
        <li>1 onion (chopped)</li>
        <li>2 cloves garlic (minced)</li>
        <li>Ground beef</li>
        <li>Salt and pepper</li>
        <li>Cooking oil</li>
    </ul>

    <!-- This is the method section -->
    <h2>Method</h2>

    <!-- Ordered list for step-by-step procedure -->
    <ol>
        <li>Boil water in a pot and cook the spaghetti according to the package instructions.</li>
        <li>Heat oil in a pan and sauté the onion and garlic.</li>
        <li>Add the ground beef and cook until brown.</li>
        <li>Pour the tomato sauce and let it simmer for 10 minutes.</li>
        <li>Add salt and pepper to taste.</li>
        <li>Drain the spaghetti and mix it with the sauce.</li>
        <li>Serve hot and enjoy your meal.</li>
    </ol>

</body>
</html>
